\[\bm{\Sigma}_{ii}=\mathbb{E}[h_{i}(\bm{z})h_{i}(\bm{z})^{\mathsf{T}}]\ \,\ \ \bm{\Sigma}_{jj}=\mathbb{E}[h_{j}(\bm{z})h_{j}(\bm{z})^{\mathsf{T}}]\ \,\ \ \bm{\Sigma}_{ij}=\mathbb{E}[h_{i}(\bm{z})h_{j}(\bm{z})^{\mathsf{T}}],\] (2.4)

